# Systems

Core game systems and managers.

## Files to Create

- **CollisionSystem.lua** - Collision detection and resolution
- **SpawnManager.lua** - Enemy and power-up spawning
- **ScoreSystem.lua** - Score tracking and management
- **ParticleSystem.lua** - Particle effects manager
- **CameraShake.lua** - Screen shake effects

Ask @physics for collision, @gameplay for spawning/scoring, @graphics for particles!
